defaultBusiness Rates
defaultLeeds has
default welcomed the retention of 
default50% of 
defaultbusiness rates
default beyond an agreed baseline
default, but 
defaultbelieves
default that 
defaultlocal authorities should be able to retain
default 100%
default of rates collected
default. This would further incen
