default authorities to borrow more to fund infrastructure projects. If borrowing rates for Combined Authorities were equalised with those available to LEPs then there would be less demand placed on those LEPs for them to borrow on their behalf, freeing LEPs to co
defaultncentrate on other priorities.
defaultThere is less of a need for new funding,
default with 
defaultyields on 
defaultbonds
default low and crowd sourcing carrying risks as yet unevaluated
