defaulta single pot for each authority, utilising a new acc
defaultounting officer function at the Combined Authority level
default (see above)
default to ensure accountability. The current system of funds, which includes 36 streams for housing alone, is cumbersome and 
defaultinefficient.
defaultTher
defaulte could also be more done to relieve the need for borrowing by relaxing the rules around commercial returns on fees and charges. For example the current arrangements 
defaultto ringfence
